learning_outcomes.en:
Course will give students:
*	knowledge of different multivariate statistical methods, their application possibilities and interpretation of the gained results;
*	knowledge and skills of applying multivariate analysis using software packages;
*	skills and experiences to find suitable data for statistical data analysis, how to systemise and prepare data for multivariate analysis;
*	skills how to carry out parametric and non-parametric multivariate statistical analysis, interpret results of statistical data analysis, how to generalise findings to the research questions and how to present research results.
